DB["Set out on a journey across all of Azeroth. Explore its distant corners, complete grand quests, and face powerful monsters in every land. This trial is long, unforgiving, and only the most patient adventurers will see it through to the end.\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:448|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Hogger] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 10|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:3655|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Mad Magglish] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 17|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:774803|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Blackfathom Ascendant] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 21|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:11921|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Besseleth] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 21|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:772529|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Son of Arugal] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 22|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:610896|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Cahooey the Big] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 29|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:522|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Mor'Ladim] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 30|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:1364|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Balgaras the Foul] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 31|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:2597|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Lord Falconcrest] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 40|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:5760|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Lord Azrethoc] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 40|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:4339|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Brimgore] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 41|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hascensiondb:npc:2745|hYou must kill |cffffff00[Ambassador Infernus] |cffffffffbefore reaching level 42|r. |cffffff00(Click Here!) |cffffffff |r|h\n\n|Hasc